.DT
shields
Discworld command help
shields

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
shields - Check the status of your arcane shields.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
shields
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
The command gives you the status of your arcane shields,
be they given by your god or created by magical means.
.EP

.SH Example
.SI 5
> shields
Shield status:
  A knife and a Tsortean metal shield are floating around you.
    Carving knife: It is in excellent condition.
    Tsortean metal shield: It is in excellent condition.
  You are surrounded by a magical impact shield.
  You are protected by the power of Pishe.
.EI

